        "S_pdf_reader",
        "extract_text"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是不同角色。Services里的那个是运行时服务实例，负责实际调度；Plugins里的是具体实现，提供extract_text能力。Service会通过uses关系去调用Plugin。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S_pdf_reader",
        "P_pdf_reader",
        "uses"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主体框架：User、API Router、Loader作为灰色节点，Plugins和Services各放一个pdf_reader节点，分别应用蓝色和橙色样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
